# Environment variables — DENSO sense website
#
# The site is a static front-end build (Vite). As of this build it requires
# NO runtime environment variables — there is nothing to configure to run
# `npm run dev` or `npm run build`.
#
# Reserved for future use (Phase 4 — demo-form backend on Azure Functions):
# the "Request a Demo" form submission destination. Uncomment and set when
# the backend is added.
#
# DEMO_FORM_DESTINATION=        # email address or CRM/webhook URL the form posts to
